value: Resident, tall dense grassland and savanna woodland: S of Sahel zone to S Angola and extending south in E South Africa, excluding forest area and much of NE Africa north of Kenya.

tall dense open grassland, grassland with bushes, and savanna woodland, including miombo, also cultivation, pastures, fallow & old cropland & damper areas eg margins of vleis & dambos;also grass-covered itronstone pans & burnt savanna;to 2500m

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
